  <brief_title>Adhesive Strips in Dermatologic Surgery: Is Cosmetic Appearance Improved?</brief_title>
  <official_title>Adhesive Strips in Dermatologic Surgery: Is Cosmetic Appearance Improved?</official_title>
  <sponsors>
