  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To determine whether the addition of adhesive stripping to a wound closed with dermal sutures
      improves outcome of wound closure. We hypothesize that the combination of adhesive strips to
      a wound closed with dermal sutures does not add significant cosmetic improvement of the
      resultant scar.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
